script.name: !job.trade.supplytrader
script.sourceplaintext:
[THIS] ->set command: COMMAND_FREETRADER target=null target2=null par1=null par2=null
if [THIS] -> get job leader START [THIS] -> delayed command COMMAND_DESTROY_THIS : arg1=null, arg2=null, arg3=null, arg4=100 return null end $temp = random value from 20000 to 300000 - 1 if [THIS] -> is docked @ = wait $temp ms else if not [THIS] -> is in active sector @ = [THIS] -> move around $temp ms end
if not random value from 0 to 9 - 1 = [THIS] -> install 1 units of Navigation Command Software MK1 = [THIS] -> install 1 units of Jumpdrive [THIS] ->set autojump active: [TRUE] [THIS] ->autojump minimum jumps= 2 [THIS] ->set jumpdrive fuel resupply: amount=40 end
Restart: $sector = [THIS] -> get homesector skip if ! $sector OR $sector == [SECTOR] @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector.simple : sector=$sector $maxrounds = random value from 300 to 800 - 1 $max.jumps = [THIS] -> get job jump range $trys = 0 $rounds = 0
$locked = table alloc $exclude = table alloc
while 1 @ = wait 10 ms gosub sub.Refuel $temp = [THIS] -> get hull percent if $temp < 50 @ = [THIS] -> call script !ship.cmd.moverepair.std : fly to this and repair=null end [THIS] ->set command: COMMAND_FREETRADER target=null target2=null par1=null par2=null @ = wait randomly from 500 to 1000 ms if not random value from 0 to 100 - 1 $max.jumps = [THIS] -> get job jump range $max.jumps = random value from 1 to $max.jumps - 1 end [THIS] ->set destination to null gosub sub.CleanExclude if [DOCKEDAT] if [DOCKEDAT] -> has a free ship dock port: ship subtype = [THIS] @ $waittime = [THIS] -> call script !lib.job.getidletime : $waittime = $waittime * 1000 @ = wait $waittime ms end [THIS] ->reset flight time else @ = [THIS] -> move around 30000 ms end $shoppinglist = get warearray for [THIS] $temp = size of array $shoppinglist inc $trys = if $trys > $temp * 2 $sector = find a random sector: startsector=[SECTOR], jumps=$jumps, owner=[OWNER] [THIS] ->set destination to $sector if $sector @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector : sector=$sector end $trys = 0 continue end
inc $rounds = do if $rounds > $maxrounds goto label Restart
* Tradepart @ = wait randomly from 500 to 1000 ms $maxvol = [THIS] -> get total volume in cargo bay $freevolumen = [THIS] -> get free volume of cargo bay $temp = random value from 50 to 200 - 1 $shoppinglist = [THIS] -> get tradeable ware array from ship $wcount = size of array $shoppinglist
$should.sell = [FALSE] do if ( $maxvol - $freevolumen ) * $temp / 100 > $freevolumen AND $wcount $should.sell = [TRUE] if $trade.route if $trade.route[3] $should.sell = [TRUE] end end
if $should.sell if $trade.route $ware = $trade.route[0] $target = $trade.route[2] else $temp = random value from 0 to $wcount - 1 $ware = $shoppinglist[$temp] $price = get average price of ware $ware inc $price = if not random value from 0 to 50 - 1 $temp = get min price of ware $ware $price = random value from $temp to $price - 1 end $amount = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $jumps = 1 while $jumps < $max.jumps @ = wait 10 ms $jumps = $jumps * 2 do if $jumps > $max.jumps $jumps = $max.jumps gosub sub.GetExclude $target = find station: resource $ware with best price depend on jumps: min.price=$price, amount=$amount, max.jumps=$jumps, startsector=[SECTOR], trader=[THIS], exclude array=$arr.exclude do if $target -> exists break end if $target -> exists $target.owner = $target -> get owner race $noto = get notoriety from race [OWNER] to race $target.owner if $noto <= [Notoriety.Foe] $exclude[$target] = [TRUE] $target = null end end end if $target -> exists @ if not [THIS] -> call script !lib.npc.station.lock : Station=$target Race=[OWNER] Ware=$ware Remove?=[FALSE] $locked[$target] = [TRUE] $target = null end end
$state = 1 else gosub sub.FindTradeRoute
if $trade.route $ware = $trade.route[0] $target = $trade.route[1] else
$shoppinglist = get warearray for [THIS] $temp = size of array $shoppinglist $index = random value from 0 to $temp - 1 $ware = $shoppinglist[$index] $owner = [THIS] -> get true owner do if is ware $ware illegal in $owner sectors continue skip if [THIS] -> can transport ware $ware continue skip if [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay continue
$price = get average price of ware $ware dec $price = if not random value from 0 to 50 - 1 $temp = get max price of ware $ware $price = random value from $price to $temp - 1 end $jumps = 1 while $jumps < $max.jumps @ = wait 10 ms $jumps = $jumps * 2 do if $jumps > $max.jumps $jumps = $max.jumps
gosub sub.GetExclude $amount = [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $target = find station: product $ware with best price depend on jumps: max.price=$price, amount=$amount, max.jumps=$jumps, startsector=[SECTOR], trader=[THIS], exclude array=$arr.exclude end inc $price = * find a dock to buy from, only use this is unable find viable factory $jumps = $max.jumps $temp = find station sells: resource $ware with best price depend on jumps: max.price=$price, amount=$amount, max.jumps=$jumps, startsector=[SECTOR], trader=[THIS], exclude array=$arr.exclude dec $price = if ! $target AND $temp $target = $temp else if not $target continue end end
if $target -> exists $target.owner = $target -> get owner race $noto = get notoriety from race [OWNER] to race $target.owner if $noto <= [Notoriety.Foe] $exclude[$target] = [TRUE] $trade.route = null $target = null continue end @ if not [THIS] -> call script !lib.npc.station.lock : Station=$target Race=[OWNER] Ware=$ware Remove?=[FALSE] $locked[$target] = [TRUE] $trade.route = null $target = null continue end end
$sector = $target -> get sector $state = -1 end $shoppinglist = null
skip if $target -> exists continue
$trys = 0 if $state == 1 [THIS] ->set command: COMMAND_SELL_WARE target=$ware target2=$target par1=$amount par2=null else [THIS] ->set command: COMMAND_GET_WARE target=$ware target2=$target par1=$amount par2=null end [THIS] ->set destination to $target
gosub sub.Refuel @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetostation : station=$target
skip if $target -> exists continue
skip if $target == [DOCKEDAT] continue
@ = [THIS] -> call script !lib.npc.station.lock : Station=[DOCKEDAT] Race=[OWNER] Ware=$ware Remove?=[TRUE]
$cprice = $target -> get price of ware $ware if $trade.route $price = $trade.route[3] if $price AND $cprice < $price $trade.route = null continue end else skip if ( $cprice - $price ) * $state >= 0 continue end
* reset the locked exclude table $locked = table alloc if $state == 1 $trueamount = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $freevolumen = $target -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay skip if $trueamount <= $freevolumen $trueamount = $freevolumen $wcount = [THIS] -> sell $trueamount units of $ware $trade.route = null else $trueamount = $target -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $freevolumen = [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay skip if $trueamount <= $freevolumen $trueamount = $freevolumen $cprice = $target -> get price of ware $ware $wcount = [THIS] -> buy $trueamount units of $ware to a max. price of $price Cr do if $wcount AND $trade.route $trade.route[3] = $cprice end
end return null * changelog: * 5: changed bestbuy/bestsell, enabled trading with docks * 6.: moved hull check up to this script for performance reasons * 7.: changed price variation for dock trading
sub.GetExclude: $table.merged = merge tables, $exclude, $locked, null, null, null $arr.exclude = get keys: table=$table.merged endsub
sub.CleanExclude: @ = wait 100 ms $sub.key = get next key: table=$exclude key=null while $sub.key $sub.next = get next key: table=$exclude key=$sub.key
if not $sub.key -> exists remove key $sub.key from table $exclude end
$sub.key = $sub.next end endsub
sub.FindTradeRoute: [THIS] ->set local variable: name='trade.route' value=null $trade.route = null $shoppinglist = get warearray for [THIS] while size of array $shoppinglist @ = wait 100 ms
$temp = size of array $shoppinglist $index = random value from 0 to $temp - 1 $ware = $shoppinglist[$index] remove element from array $shoppinglist at index $index
do if is ware $ware illegal in [TRUEOWNER] sectors continue skip if [THIS] -> can transport ware $ware continue skip if [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay continue gosub sub.GetExclude $amount = [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Jumpdrive in cargo bay $jumps = $max.jumps else $jumps = $max.jumps / 2 end $price = get min price of ware $ware $dest.target = find station: resource $ware with best price depend on jumps: min.price=$price, amount=$amount, max.jumps=$jumps, startsector=[SECTOR], trader=[THIS], exclude array=$arr.exclude @ = wait 10 ms if $dest.target -> exists $price = $dest.target -> get price of ware $ware dec $price = $station.amount = $dest.target -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $buy.amount = get minimum, $amount, $station.amount, null, null, null $source.target = find station: product $ware with best price depend on jumps: max.price=$price, amount=$buy.amount, max.jumps=$max.jumps, startsector=[SECTOR], trader=[THIS], exclude array=$arr.exclude do if $source.target -> exists break end end @ = wait 1000 ms if $dest.target -> exists if $source.target -> exists $trade.route = create new array, size=4, elements=$ware, $source.target, $dest.target, [FALSE], null, null, null, null [THIS] ->set local variable: name='trade.route' value=$trade.route end end endsub
sub.Refuel: if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Jumpdrive in cargo bay $got.energy = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $needed = [THIS] ->get needed jump energy: jumps=10 if $needed > $got.energy $needed = [THIS] ->get needed jump energy: jumps=40 $needed = $needed - $got.energy @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.resupply.self : Ware to Resupply=Energy Cells Quantity=$needed Max Fly Range=3 @ = wait randomly from 5000 to 10000 ms @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.undock : @ = wait 500 ms end end endsub
return null
